Information posters should be posted in conspicuous
places around the reception desk during influenza sea
son to promptly identify patients with ILI (Figure 3).
These patients should be instructed of cough etiquette,
and lead to waiting room after providing them with
masks to wear. Patients are to sit more than 1 m away
from each other. Movement should be minimized to
reduce the opportunity of contact with other patients.
